If nï4 and mï2, the list is {2,4,3,1}: 
count 1, 2, execute 2, leaving 1, 3, 4;
count 3, 4, execute 4, leaving 1, 3;
count 1, 3, execute 3, leaving 1;
count 1, 1, execute 1:
JosephusList[4,2]
{2,4,3,1}
